items.title: Amtrak launches faster, updated Acela train service as Trump admin takes DC Union Station control
items.description: NextGen Acela train service offers premium travel with free Wi-Fi, USB ports and 27% more seats on the Washington-New York-Boston corridor.

items.title: Southwest rolls out new conditions for plus-size passenger refunds
items.description: Plus-size travelers must buy extra seats on Southwest flights with assigned seating, with refunds only available if flights depart with open seats.
